The course improves the students' oral and written communication skills at level C1. The precondition for taking the course is knowledge of Estonian at intermediate level (B2).Objectives/eesmärkid:  To improve the oral and written communication skills at level C1 and language use in different functional styles.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  By the end of the course the student
- can differentiate between general and special language
- can describe, discuss, express opinions and comment within the scope of the subjects covered during the course while using knowledge of the language purposefully
- can write a short note, form statements and write a resumé.
